atas kembalinya Anda ke Yihousheng.

234
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:40,030
Aku berharap padamu

235
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:41,630
cerah

236
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:43,650
dan masa depan yang tak terbatas.

237
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:46,030
Saya permisi dulu.

238
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,520
Tidak perlu mengantarku keluar.

239
00:12:08,290 --> 00:12:13,600
