B-Biar saya lihat dulu.

370
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,640
Anda bisa melihat sekeliling Anda.

371
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,680
Berlangsung.

372
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:09,520
Zhengyou.

373
