Tenang saja.

535
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:52,240
Saya pasti akan membuat tinta yang
memenuhi standar tertinggi Li Ink.

536
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:55,110
Saat itu,
aku akan bersaing denganmu secara adil dan jujur.

537
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:07,750
Ronghua.

538
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:10,550
Ronghua.

539
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:11,590
Ronghua...

